1.Visualization (ggplot)

library(tidyverse)
library(gapminder)

1 Basic Plots

1.1 Scatter Plots

gapminder_2007 <- gapminder %>%
  filter(year == 2007)

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp)) + 
  geom_point()

1.2 Line Graphs

total_pop <- gapminder %>%
  group_by(year) %>%
  summarize(pop = sum(as.numeric(pop)))

ggplot(total_pop, aes(x=year, y=pop)) + 
  geom_line()

1.3 Bar Graphs

1.3.1 Two Factor

life_by_cont <- gapminder %>%
  filter(year==2007) %>%
  group_by(continent) %>%
  summarize(mean_life = mean(lifeExp))

ggplot(life_by_cont, aes(x=continent, y=mean_life)) + 
  geom_col()

1.3.2 One Factor

country_count <- gapminder %>%
  filter(year==2007)
  
ggplot(country_count, aes(x=continent)) + 
  geom_bar()

1.4 Histograms

1.4.1 Automatic

gapminder_2007 <- gapminder %>%
  filter(year==2007)

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x = lifeExp)) +
  geom_histogram()

1.4.2 Set bins

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x = lifeExp)) +
  geom_histogram(binwidth = 10)

1.5 Box Plots

gapminder_2007 <- gapminder %>%
  filter(year==2007)

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x = continent, y = lifeExp)) +
  geom_boxplot()

2 Advanced

2.1 Example

2.1.1 Basic Scatter Plot

gapminder_2007 <- gapminder %>%
  filter(year == 2007)

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp)) + 
  geom_point()

2.1.2 Scaling an axis

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  scale_x_log10()

2.1.3 Adding color

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp, color=continent)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  scale_x_log10()

2.1.4 Adding size

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp, color=continent, size=pop)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  scale_x_log10()

2.1.5 Setting axis limit

ggplot(gapminder_2007, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp, color=continent, size=pop)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  scale_x_log10() + 
  expand_limits(y=30)

2.1.6 Faceting

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp, color=continent, size=pop)) + 
  geom_point() +
  scale_x_log10() +
  facet_wrap(~ year)

2.1.7 Labeling

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp, color=continent, size=pop)) + 
  geom_point() +
  scale_x_log10() +
  facet_wrap(~ year) +
  labs(
    x = "GDP Per Capita",
    y = "Life Expectancy",
    title = "Growing GDP and Life Expectancy",
    subtitle = "Converging Global Trends",
    caption = "Gapminder, 2017")

2.1.8 Themes

ggplot(gapminder, aes(x=gdpPercap, y=lifeExp, color=continent, size=pop)) + 
  geom_point() +
  scale_x_log10() +
  facet_wrap(~ year) +
  labs(
    x = "GDP Per Capita",
    y = "Life Expectancy",
    title = "Growing GDP and Life Expectancy",
    subtitle = "Converging Global Trends",
    caption = "Gapminder, 2017") +
  theme_bw()

theme(text = element_text(family = "Bookman"),
    title = element_text(color = "gray25"),
    plot.subtitle = element_text(size = 12))

theme_myproject <- function() {
  theme_bw() +
  theme(text = element_text(family = "Bookman", color = "gray25"))}
